 for six months but looks forward enough for the return after a minor placing in a recent trial. Blessed with plenty of speed so can take full advantage of the inside barrier for a winning return. 9. BOULEVARDOFDREAMS has had two runs this prep and is yet to finish in the top three but both have been in higher-graded races. The driver has some work to do from this wide starting position but her fitness will be building and she is better placed. 7. HES CHARLIES ANGEL led and faded last time but still wasn't too far off the winner and had recorded a series of solid efforts prior so is capable of better. 6. FE FE ON FIRE is hard to knock off back-to-back wins at this circuit and distance, last week racing wide but proving too good.\",\"runners\":[1,9,7,6],\"exclusive\":false}","tips":{"tipType":"Standard","tipster":"Fred Hastings","tipRunnerNumbers":[1,6,8,5]},"ratings":[{"ratingType":"Rating","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,7,4]},{"ratingType":"Last12Months","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,1,9,6]},{"ratingType":"Recent","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,6,2,4]},{"ratingType":"Distance","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,5,6]},{"ratingType":"Class","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,5,9,6]},{"ratingType":"Time","ratingRunnerNumbers":[10,9,6,2]},{"ratingType":"Overall","ratingRunnerNumbers":[1,9,6,10]}],"multiLegApproximates":[],"betTypes":[{"wageringProduct":"Win","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Place","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Quinella","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Exacta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Duet","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"Trifecta","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"FirstFour","firstLeg":{"raceNumber":6,"venueMnemonic":"MEN","raceType":"H"}},{"wageringProduct":"